---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="Vasif Asadov | Data Scientist & AI Researcher">
  
  <section class="flex flex-col-reverse lg:flex-row gap-12 lg:gap-20 items-center mb-32 mt-12">
    <div class="flex-1 space-y-8">
      <div class="space-y-2">
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-400 via-cyan-400 to-purple-500 bg-clip-text text-transparent tracking-tight pb-2">
          Vasif Asadov
        </h1>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium text-slate-300">
          Data Scientist <span class="text-teal-500">|</span> Control & Automation Engineer
        </h2>
      </div>
      
      <div class="text-slate-400 space-y-5 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          I am Vasif Asadov, a Data Scientist and Master's student in Control and Automation Engineering at Yildiz Technical University. My analytical foundation was established early — a perfect score of 700/700 on the Azerbaijan National Entrance Exam earned me a Presidential Scholarship, and that same precision carries into everything I build today.
        </p>
        <p>
          My path into data science is rooted in real engineering experience. At SOCAR, one of the region's largest energy companies, I worked hands-on with SQL Server for data management and plant automation systems. That foundation led me to a 6-month Full Stack Data Science internship, where I took ownership of the entire ML pipeline — from raw data cleaning to model deployment using <strong class="text-slate-200 font-semibold">Python, SQL, R, and Tableau</strong>.
        </p>
        <p>
          Currently, my Master's thesis sits at the intersection of deep learning and control theory: <strong class="text-teal-400 font-semibold">AI-based Model Predictive Control of Nonlinear Systems</strong>. I am drawn to problems where rigorous engineering meets modern machine learning — building systems that are not just accurate, but production-ready, automated, and built to last.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="relative w-56 h-56 md:w-80 md:h-80 shrink-0 group">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-tr from-teal-500 to-purple-500 rounded-full blur-2xl opacity-40 group-hover:opacity-60 transition-opacity duration-500"></div>
      <img src="/images/profile.png" alt="Vasif Asadov - Data Scientist" class="relative w-full h-full object-cover rounded-full border-4 border-slate-800 shadow-2xl z-10" />
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-32 space-y-20">
    
    <div>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-10">
        <span class="w-10 h-1 bg-teal-500 rounded-full"></span>
        <h3 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight">Experience</h3>
      </div>
      
      <div class="space-y-10 border-l-2 border-teal-500/20 ml-4 pl-8 md:pl-10">
        
        <div class="relative group">
          <div class="absolute -left-[43px] md:-left-[51px] top-2 w-5 h-5 bg-teal-500 rounded-full ring-4 ring-slate-900 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform"></div>
          <div class="bg-slate-800/40 p-6 md:p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-700/50 hover:border-teal-500/50 transition-colors shadow-sm hover:shadow-md">
            <span class="inline-block text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-teal-400 mb-3 bg-teal-900/30 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Jul 2025 - Jan 2026</span>
            <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-1">Data Scientist Intern</h4>
            <p class="text-slate-400 font-medium mb-5">Data Science Academy <span class="mx-2">•</span> Remote</p>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-base text-slate-300 list-none">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-teal-500 mt-1">▹</span> Conducted exploratory data analysis and advanced preprocessing for end-to-end ML workflows.</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-teal-500 mt-1">▹</span> Built and optimized models using Python and Scikit-Learn (cross-validation, hyperparameter tuning).</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-teal-500 mt-1">▹</span> Developed interactive Power BI and Tableau dashboards to present model outputs and business KPIs.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="relative group">
          <div class="absolute -left-[43px] md:-left-[51px] top-2 w-5 h-5 bg-slate-600 rounded-full ring-4 ring-slate-900 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform"></div>
          <div class="bg-slate-800/30 p-6 md:p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-700/50 hover:border-slate-500 transition-colors">
            <span class="inline-block text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-400 mb-3 bg-slate-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Mar 2023 - May 2023</span>
            <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-1">Data Management Intern</h4>
            <p class="text-slate-400 font-medium mb-5">R&D Institute of Oil and Gas (SOCAR) <span class="mx-2">•</span> Baku</p>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-base text-slate-300 list-none">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-slate-400 mt-1">▹</span> Managed, validated, and optimized plant sensor data in Microsoft SQL Server.</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-slate-400 mt-1">▹</span> Developed automated SQL triggers for threshold-based alerts, improving monitoring efficiency.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

    <div>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-10">
        <span class="w-10 h-1 bg-purple-500 rounded-full"></span>
        <h3 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight">Education</h3>
      </div>
      
      <div class="space-y-10 border-l-2 border-purple-500/20 ml-4 pl-8 md:pl-10">
        
        <div class="relative group">
          <div class="absolute -left-[43px] md:-left-[51px] top-2 w-5 h-5 bg-purple-500 rounded-full ring-4 ring-slate-900 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform"></div>
          <div class="bg-slate-800/40 p-6 md:p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-700/50 hover:border-purple-500/50 transition-colors shadow-sm">
            <span class="inline-block text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-purple-400 mb-3 bg-purple-900/30 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Current</span>
            <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-1">Master's in Control & Automation Eng.</h4>
            <p class="text-slate-400 font-medium mb-5">Yildiz Technical University <span class="mx-2">•</span> Istanbul, TR</p>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-base text-slate-300 list-none">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-purple-500 mt-1">▹</span> Fully Funded Türkiye Scholarship.</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-purple-500 mt-1">▹</span> Thesis: Deep Learning Based Model Predictive Control of Nonlinear Systems.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="relative group">
          <div class="absolute -left-[43px] md:-left-[51px] top-2 w-5 h-5 bg-slate-600 rounded-full ring-4 ring-slate-900 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform"></div>
          <div class="bg-slate-800/30 p-6 md:p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-700/50 hover:border-slate-500 transition-colors">
            <span class="inline-block text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-400 mb-3 bg-slate-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Sep 2018 - Jun 2023</span>
            <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-1">Bachelor's in Process Automation Eng.</h4>
            <p class="text-slate-400 font-medium mb-5">Baku Higher Oil School <span class="mx-2">•</span> Baku, AZ</p>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-base text-slate-300 list-none">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-slate-400 mt-1">▹</span> Azerbaijan Presidency Scholarship.</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-slate-400 mt-1">▹</span> Graduated with High Honors (GPA: 3.5/4.0).</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

  </section>
<section class="mb-32">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-10 text-center justify-center">
      <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight">Technical Arsenal</h3>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      
      <div class="bg-slate-800/40 border border-slate-700/50 p-6 rounded-2xl hover:bg-slate-800 transition-all">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-900/50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4" /></svg>
        </div>
        <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">Programming</h4>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-900 text-slate-300 text-sm rounded-lg border border-slate-700">Python</span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-900 text-slate-300 text-sm rounded-lg border border-slate-700">R</span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-900 text-slate-300 text-sm rounded-lg border border-slate-700">Bash & Fish Shell</span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-900 text-slate-300 text-sm rounded-lg border border-slate-700">LaTeX</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-slate-800/40 border border-slate-700/50 p-6 rounded-2xl hover:bg-slate-800 transition-all">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-indigo-900/50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-indigo-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0zM10 7v3m0 0v3m0-3h3m-3 0H7" /></svg>
        </div>
        <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">Data Wrangling</h4>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-900 text-slate-300 text-sm rounded-lg border border-slate-700">Pandas & Polars</span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-900 text-slate-300 text-sm rounded-lg border border-slate-700">Advanced SQL</span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-900 text-slate-300 text-sm rounded-lg border border-slate-700">Feature Engineering</span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-900 text-slate-300 text-sm rounded-lg border border-slate-700">ETL / ELT Pipelines</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-slate-800/40 border border-slate-700/50 p-6 rounded-2xl hover:bg-slate-800 transition-all">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-900/50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 7v10c0 2.21 3.582 4 8 4s8-1.79 8-4V7M4 7c0 2.21 3.582 4 8 4s8-1.79 8-4M4 7c0-2.21 3.582-4 8-4s8 1.79 8 4m0 5c0 2.21-3.582 4-8 4s-8-1.79-8-4" /></svg>
        </div>
        <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">Database Architecture</h4>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-900 text-slate-300 text-sm rounded-lg border border-slate-700">T-SQL & PL/SQL</span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-900 text-slate-300 text-sm rounded-lg border border-slate-700">PostgreSQL & MySQL</span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-900 text-slate-300 text-sm rounded-lg border border-slate-700">DuckDB (OLAP)</span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-900 text-slate-300 text-sm rounded-lg border border-slate-700">MS SQL Server</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-slate-800/40 border border-slate-700/50 p-6 rounded-2xl hover:bg-slate-800 transition-all md:col-span-2">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-emerald-900/50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-emerald-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z" /></svg>
        </div>
        <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">ML & Deep Learning Architectures</h4>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-900 text-slate-300 text-sm rounded-lg border border-slate-700">PyTorch & TensorFlow</span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-900 text-slate-300 text-sm rounded-lg border border-slate-700">Predictive Modeling</span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-900 text-slate-300 text-sm rounded-lg border border-slate-700">Unsupervised Learning</span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-900 text-slate-300 text-sm rounded-lg border border-slate-700">Dimensionality Reduction (PCA, t-SNE)</span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-900 text-slate-300 text-sm rounded-lg border border-slate-700">CNN Architectures</span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-900 text-slate-300 text-sm rounded-lg border border-slate-700">Ensemble Methods</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-slate-800/40 border border-slate-700/50 p-6 rounded-2xl hover:bg-slate-800 transition-all md:col-span-1">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-pink-900/50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-pink-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 7h6m0 10v-3m-3 3h.01M9 17h.01M9 14h.01M12 14h.01M15 11h.01M12 11h.01M9 11h.01M7 21h10a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0 002 2z" /></svg>
        </div>
        <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">Statistical Fundamentals</h4>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-900 text-slate-300 text-sm rounded-lg border border-slate-700">Inferential Statistics</span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-900 text-slate-300 text-sm rounded-lg border border-slate-700">Probability Distributions</span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-900 text-slate-300 text-sm rounded-lg border border-slate-700">A/B Testing & Experimentation</span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-900 text-slate-300 text-sm rounded-lg border border-slate-700">Hypothesis Testing</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-slate-800/40 border border-slate-700/50 p-6 rounded-2xl hover:bg-slate-800 transition-all md:col-span-1">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-amber-900/50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-amber-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M11 3.055A9.001 9.001 0 1020.945 13H11V3.055z" /><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M20.488 9H15V3.512A9.025 9.025 0 0120.488 9z" /></svg>
        </div>
        <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">BI & Interactive Analytics</h4>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-900 text-slate-300 text-sm rounded-lg border border-slate-700">Power BI & Tableau</span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-900 text-slate-300 text-sm rounded-lg border border-slate-700">Apache Superset</span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-900 text-slate-300 text-sm rounded-lg border border-slate-700">Plotly Dash</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-slate-800/40 border border-slate-700/50 p-6 rounded-2xl hover:bg-slate-800 transition-all md:col-span-1">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-cyan-900/50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-cyan-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 15a4 4 0 004 4h9a5 5 0 10-.1-9.999 5.002 5.002 0 10-9.78 2.096A4.001 4.001 0 003 15z" /></svg>
        </div>
        <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">Cloud Computing & MLOps</h4>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-900 text-slate-300 text-sm rounded-lg border border-slate-700">AWS Core (S3, EC2, IAM)</span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-900 text-slate-300 text-sm rounded-lg border border-slate-700">Snowflake & Databricks</span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-900 text-slate-300 text-sm rounded-lg border border-slate-700">Docker Containerization</span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-900 text-slate-300 text-sm rounded-lg border border-slate-700">CI/CD Pipelines</span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-900 text-slate-300 text-sm rounded-lg border border-slate-700">Git Version Control</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-slate-800/40 border border-slate-700/50 p-6 rounded-2xl hover:bg-slate-800 transition-all md:col-span-1">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-rose-900/50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-rose-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 12a9 9 0 01-9 9m9-9a9 9 0 00-9-9m9 9H3m9 9a9 9 0 01-9-9m9 9c1.657 0 3-4.03 3-9s-1.343-9-3-9m0 18c-1.657 0-3-4.03-3-9s1.343-9 3-9m-9 9a9 9 0 019-9" /></svg>
        </div>
        <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">Web & Technical Docs</h4>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-900 text-slate-300 text-sm rounded-lg border border-slate-700">Astro Framework</span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-900 text-slate-300 text-sm rounded-lg border border-slate-700">Tailwind CSS</span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-900 text-slate-300 text-sm rounded-lg border border-slate-700">Markdown & MDX</span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-900 text-slate-300 text-sm rounded-lg border border-slate-700">GitHub Pages</span>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
<section class="mb-32">
    <div class="flex justify-between items-end mb-10 border-b border-slate-800 pb-4">
      <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight">Certifications</h3>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-5">
      
      {[
        { title: "Microsoft Certified: Power BI Analyst", desc: "PL-300 Associate Certificate", link: "/certificates/ms_powerbi.pdf" },
        { title: "Full Stack Data Scientist", desc: "Data Science Academy Certificate", link: "/certificates/data_science_academy_certificate.pdf" },
        { title: "Talent Report Snapshot", desc: "One-Page Performance Summary", link: "/certificates/talent_report_snapshot.pdf" },
        { title: "Data Talent Report", desc: "Full Technical & Soft Skill Evaluation", link: "/certificates/vasif_asadov_talent_report.pdf" },
        { title: "Advanced SQL Certification", desc: "BTK Academy Professional Development", link: "/certificates/sql_certificate.pdf" },
        { title: "TOEFL iBT Score Report", desc: "English Proficiency (C1 Level)", link: "/certificates/vasif_asadov_toefl.pdf" }
      ].map((cert) => (
        <a href={cert.link} target="_blank" 
           class="group grid grid-cols-[auto_1fr] gap-4 p-5 bg-slate-800/40 border border-slate-700/50 rounded-2xl hover:border-teal-500/50 hover:bg-slate-800 transition-all shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:-translate-y-1 items-start">
          
          {/* İkon Konteynırı - Küçülmemesi için shrink-0 ekledik */}
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-slate-900 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-teal-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z" />
            </svg>
          </div>

          {/* Metin Alanı - Taşmaları önlemek için min-w-0 ekledik */}
          <div class="min-w-0">
            <strong class="block text-white group-hover:text-teal-400 transition-colors truncate sm:whitespace-normal break-words leading-tight">
                {cert.title}
            </strong>
            <span class="block text-sm text-slate-400 mt-1 leading-snug">
                {cert.desc}
            </span>
          </div>
        </a>
      ))}

    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-20">
    <div class="bg-slate-900 rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12 border border-slate-800 shadow-2xl relative overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 -mr-20 -mt-20 w-64 h-64 bg-teal-500/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
      
      <div class="relative z-10">
        <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Explore The Knowledge Base</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-400 mb-10 max-w-2xl text-lg">This platform serves as my official digital garden. A structured environment where rigorous research meets production-ready code.</p>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          
          <div class="bg-slate-800/50 border border-slate-700/50 p-6 rounded-2xl hover:border-teal-500/30 transition-colors">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-teal-400 mb-2">Data Analysis</h4>
            <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Comprehensive projects covering complex queries across multiple engines (<strong class="text-slate-200">T-SQL, PL/SQL, DuckDB</strong>) and interactive BI dashboards.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-slate-800/50 border border-slate-700/50 p-6 rounded-2xl hover:border-purple-500/30 transition-colors">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-purple-400 mb-2">Data Science</h4>
            <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Advanced implementation of Regression, Classification, and Clustering models, focusing heavily on building robust <strong class="text-slate-200">end-to-end ML pipelines</strong>.</p>
          </div>

